'''Samawa FC''' ({{lang-ar|'''نادي السماوة'''}}), is an Iraqi sports club based in [[Samawa|As-Samawa]], [[Muthanna Governorate|Al-Muthanna]], Iraq, which plays in the [[Iraqi Premier League]],<ref>[http://www.azzaman.com/?p=117403 Samawa wins the title of first division championship and qualify for the Premier League]</ref> the top tier of the Iraqi football. The club's home stadium is [[As Samawah Stadium]].

