'''Al Mina'a Stadium''', is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Basra]], [[Iraq]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and served as the home stadium of [[Al Minaa]].  The stadium holds 10,000 people. 

