'''College of Staten Island Baseball Complex''' is a [[stadium]] in [[Staten Island, New York]].  It is primarily used for [[baseball]] and was the home of [[Staten Island Yankees]] before they moved to [[Richmond County Bank Ballpark]] in 2001.  The ballpark had a capacity of 2,500 people and opened in 1999.<ref name="athletic_facilities">{{cite web|url=http://www.csidolphins.com/Sports/gen/2006/Directions-Facilities.asp?taba=4&tab=ath|title=College of Staten Island Athletics|accessdate=2009-07-12}}</ref>  It currently hosts the [[College of Staten Island]] Dolphins baseball team.<ref name="athletic_facilities"/>

