'''Edward Moss''' (born 9 June 1988) is an international [[association football|footballer]] from the [[British Virgin Islands]], who plays as a midfielder for the [[British Virgin Islands national football team]] and the L.A. Wolves. A hard working, creative player known for his assists and long range goals.
